[SHORT DESC]
Heals 25% HP when hit by a Water-type attack. 
[LONG DESC]
<p>When this Pok√©mon is hit by a Water-type attack, it gains 25% of its max HP. No secondary effects associated with the Water-type attack will occur. If Protect is successfully used against a Water-type attack, Water Absorb does not activate. If Substitute is used against a Water-type attack, Water Absorb does activate.</p>